N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 565.4 - List of records

State Regulations

On behalf of the office, the records access officer shall
maintain a reasonably detailed current list by subject matter of all records in
the possession of the agency, whether or not available under Public Officers

Law, article 6 and this Part. Notes
